Completed 2026-06-21.

Files created:
- src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Membership/Models/MembershipResponse.cs
  Authoritative response shape per design.md Part 1 §"Endpoint contract":
  (EntityType, PersonIdentity, Ids, ByRole, Count, CacheExpiresAt, ContinuationToken?).
  Self-locked JSON contract via [property: JsonPropertyName("camelCase")] on every
  positional parameter (independent of host JsonSerializerOptions config so the
  shape is stable in tests + logger contexts).
