  10 tests covering: camelCase top-level, camelCase nested personIdentity, GUID
  string D-form, ISO 8601 DateTimeOffset, explicit `continuationToken: null`,
  preserved empty arrays in byRole, full roundtrip top-level, full roundtrip
  PersonIdentity, continuationToken-present serialization, roundtrip with token.

